@startuml OpenBooks System Sequence
title OpenBooks 

actor User
participant "Dashboard\n(Next.js UI)" as UI
participant "Next.js API" as API
participant "Plaid API" as Plaid
database "Postgres" as DB
participant "Classification\nAgent" as Agent

== Auth ==
User -> UI : Enter password
UI -> API : POST /api/auth
API -> API : Verify password, set cookie
API --> UI : 200 + Set-Cookie
UI --> User : Dashboard

User -> UI : Click Logout
UI -> API : POST /api/auth/logout
API -> API : Clear cookie
API --> UI : redirect to login

== Link bank (one-time) ==
User -> UI : Click "Link bank"
UI -> API : GET /api/plaid/status
API -> DB : Check plaid_link_state (or token file)
DB --> API : linked / not linked
API --> UI : { linked }
alt Not linked
  UI -> API : GET /api/plaid/link-token
  API -> Plaid : Create link_token (client_id, secret)
  Plaid --> API : link_token
  API --> UI : { link_token }
  UI -> UI : Open Plaid Link (popup)
  User -> UI : Select institution, complete Link
  UI -> API : POST /api/plaid/exchange { public_token }
  API -> Plaid : Exchange public_token for access_token
  Plaid --> API : access_token, item_id
  API -> DB : Store access_token (plaid_link_state / file)
  API --> UI : { success: true }
  UI --> User : Bank linked
end

== Sync transactions (manual or cron) ==
User -> UI : Click Sync (or cron hits API)
UI -> API : GET /api/plaid/sync
API -> DB : SELECT cursor FROM sync_state
DB --> API : cursor
loop Until has_more = false
  API -> Plaid : transactionsSync(access_token, cursor)
  Plaid --> API : added, modified, removed, next_cursor
  API -> DB : Upsert transactions; delete removed; UPDATE sync_state
end
API --> UI : { added, modified, removed, syncedAt }
UI --> User : Sync complete

== Read data (dashboard tabs) ==
User -> UI : Open tab (Transactions / Income / Deductions / etc.)
UI -> API : GET /api/transactions | /api/income | /api/deductions | ...
API -> DB : SELECT from transactions | income | deductions | rules | mileage
DB --> API : rows
API --> UI : JSON
UI --> User : Render table

== Classify (agent) ==
User -> UI : Click "Classify" (or "Clear" then "Classify")
opt Clear first
  User -> UI : Click "Clear"
  UI -> API : POST /api/agent/clear
  API -> DB : Truncate income, deductions, uncategorized
  API --> UI : 200
end
UI -> API : POST /api/agent/run
API -> Agent : POST {AGENT_URL}/run (with API key)
Agent -> DB : Read transactions, agent_rules, agent_prompt
Agent -> Agent : Classify into income / deduction / uncategorized
Agent -> DB : INSERT into income, deductions, uncategorized
Agent --> API : 200
API --> UI : 200
note over UI : UI polls GET /api/agent/progress for current/total
opt User cancels
  User -> UI : Click "Cancel"
  UI -> API : POST /api/agent/cancel
  API -> Agent : POST .../run/cancel
  Agent --> API : 200
  API --> UI : 200
end
UI --> User : Classification done

== Optional: CSV upload ==
User -> UI : Upload transactions or mileage CSV
UI -> API : POST /api/transactions/upload or /api/mileage/upload (multipart)
API -> DB : INSERT/upsert from parsed CSV
API --> UI : result
UI --> User : Upload complete

== Optional: Income / Deductions / Rules CRUD ==
User -> UI : Add or edit income, deduction, or rule
UI -> API : POST/PATCH/DELETE /api/income | /api/deductions | /api/rules/[id]
API -> DB : INSERT | UPDATE | DELETE
DB --> API : ok
API --> UI : 200
UI --> User : Saved

@enduml
